Titolo: Twin Eagle

Anno: 1988

Descrizione: Twin Eagle: Revenge Joe's Brother is a vertically scrolling shooter arcade game which was published in 1988. It was developed by SETA Corporation and licensed to Taito. It was one of the first arcade to use extensive digital sampling, from digitized photos to a digitized soundtrack. Controlling a helicopter, the player shoots aircraft and other attackers to earn points. If certain buildings are destroyed, hostages are found and extra points are received for saving them. A NES port was published a year later by Romstar.
Twin Eagle was followed up by a sequel in 1994, Twin Eagle II: The Rescue Mission, also by SETA.

Genere: Scrolling shooter

Valutazione: N/A
